description: Kiana Kaslana is one of many main characters in Honkai Impact 3rd. She is the daughter of Cecilia Shariac and Siegfried Kaslana. She is currently enrolled at St. Freya High School to train as a Valkyrie alongside Mei and Bronya. Though no matter where she goes, Kiana always manages to find trouble...
name: Kiana Kaslana
